transcript:
[Music]
five hidden signs of loneliness you're
scrolling on your phone even when you're
surrounded by people often that's
because you're struggling to connect
with them in person you constantly feel
tired and don't sleep well you become
overly attached to material possessions
and buying new things that you don't
need you make the effort to socialize
but when you do you feel like you don't
belong and no one really gets you you
block out those horrible feelings with
things like binge watching tv
